---
source: crates/cosmon-cli/tests/help_goldens.rs
expression: stdout
---
Audit MCP servers registered in the configured service registry

Usage: cs doctor mcp [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --config <PATH>
          Path to configuration file

      --registry <REGISTRY>
          Override the path to the service registry database.
          
          Defaults to the platform data dir used by the service registry.

  -v, --verbose
          Enable verbose output

      --json
          Output in JSON format

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
